I started rom hacking around 2000 or so and was interested in rom expansion. Every document I looked at said something along the lines of "Nes rom expansion is impossible. If you don't know how, don't try, and those that do know why." Eventually I ended up at nesdev and homebrew kinda trumped rom hacking for me.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=187">never-obsolete</a> — Tue Mar 01, 2011 8:06 am</p><hr />
